      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRINCIPAL DEALER (8) comes here with the visors replacing the blinkers following a 3.3L defeat last start. The inside draw today is a big tick for her chances and her best form stacks right up in this race. Can sit closer today and break her maiden. PRETEY ROYAL (6) finished off strongly from the back of the pack to be 1.9L off the winner most recently in a stronger maiden at Pinjarra. She may end up back in the run again, but if she can run up to that level in this event, she'll go close to winning. OBSCENTINO (1) is knocking on the door of a maiden win, missing narrowly at Pinjarra most recently. The inside draw should see him close to the speed as he was here two starts back and he can make a statement. OPAL NERO (7) was narrowly beaten in a BM44+ last start and can feature on the back of that performance. BAMBUN GIRL (4) can improve sharply getting out in trip today.",
